    Live data feed

    Our air quality monitoring station at Ecotech Head Office, Knoxfield, Melbourne, Australia, continuously monitors general air quality and related meteorological parameters.

    Live Data is available for the measurements of: Ozone (O3), Carbon Monoxide (CO), Nitrogen Dioxide (NO2), Sulphur Dioxide (SO2), Ambient temperature (AT), wind speed, wind direction and rainfall.

    Note: Data supplied for demonstration purposes only.
